WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love In A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.262
=Episode 8=

00:01:14.960 --> 00:01:15.960
Girl.

00:01:16.690 --> 00:01:17.880
I'm sorry. It's all my fault.

00:01:17.880 --> 00:01:19.780
I shouldn't have been
so harsh to you just now.

00:01:21.080 --> 00:01:22.120
Dad, it's fine.

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:24.640
Sometimes, I'm insensible too.

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:29.040
Here.

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:32.120
Eat more so that you can stay healthy.

00:01:44.600 --> 00:01:46.080
What are you doing?

00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:47.200
You terrified me.

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:57.880
Go and flirt with someone else.

00:01:57.880 --> 00:01:58.960
I'm your younger sister.

00:02:03.390 --> 00:02:04.960
What? Can't I even have some water now?

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:07.880
Do you realize

00:02:07.880 --> 00:02:10.680
how dangerous it is for you
to keep getting closer to me like this?

00:02:13.662 --> 00:02:14.600
What do you mean?

00:02:16.100 --> 00:02:17.800
We shouldn't
let anyone see us like this.

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:21.800
But now, only the two of us are here.

00:02:26.240 --> 00:02:27.800
Shu Jiajia was here.

00:02:30.600 --> 00:02:32.320
She said she saw
what happened that night.

00:02:33.460 --> 00:02:34.640
We mustn't continue like this.

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:44.440
What she saw doesn't matter.

00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:47.440
Guess what I saw?

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.880
The portrait in front of your bed,

00:02:51.880 --> 00:02:53.040
was it a portrait of me?

00:02:56.200 --> 00:02:57.040
Was it?

00:02:57.040 --> 00:02:58.920
No.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:11.920
Young Master Chen,

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:14.480
if I were you,
I would court her directly.

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:16.120
At least you won't need
to stay gloomy all alone here.

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.800
What do you know?

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:19.520
You just don't have the guts, right?

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:21.880
What?

00:03:21.880 --> 00:03:24.960
Are you afraid that she might stop
being your friend when she rejects you?

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:27.360
Do you think I don't dare to punch you?

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:29.800
I was spot-on, right?

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:31.000
What about this?

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.360
I'll assist you.

00:03:32.360 --> 00:03:33.560
You'll owe me one.

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:39.800
How will you assist me?

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:48.000
She's here.

00:03:48.412 --> 00:03:49.025
Ze.

00:03:49.025 --> 00:03:50.065
Zhu, come here.

00:03:50.065 --> 00:03:51.185
Long time no see, Qun.

00:03:51.185 --> 00:03:52.065
Sit here.

00:03:52.065 --> 00:03:52.905
Long time no see.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:55.160
Who's the guy behind her?

00:03:55.160 --> 00:03:56.480
Don't tell me it's her boyfriend.

00:03:56.480 --> 00:03:57.560
What boyfriend?

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.400
It's her stepbrother.

00:04:03.440 --> 00:04:05.120
I didn't invite you.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:06.120
Why are you here?

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:08.520
I'm here to see

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:11.080
what kind of shady friends
my sister is drinking with.

00:04:11.080 --> 00:04:12.290
What has that got to do with you?

00:04:13.537 --> 00:04:14.537
Since we're here,

00:04:14.537 --> 00:04:15.537
let's have a toast.

00:04:15.537 --> 00:04:16.577
Let's have a toast.

00:04:16.577 --> 00:04:18.137
Come on.

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:26.400
Everyone's here.

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:28.040
Let's play the King's Game.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.240
The rules are simple.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:30.560
The one who gets the King's Card

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.680
has the right to designate anyone
to do anything they want.

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:33.440
Here.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.320
Just ask her out.

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:42.520
Leave the rest to me.

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:50.840
I have

00:04:51.587 --> 00:04:52.507
the King's Card.

00:04:52.812 --> 00:04:53.812
What about this?

00:04:53.875 --> 00:04:56.995
The two who got
the Ace of Hearts and 3 of Hearts

00:04:57.000 --> 00:04:59.660
will have to kiss each other
through their fingers for 15 seconds.

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:02.200
You don't sound reliable at all.

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:03.320
Don't forget.

00:05:03.375 --> 00:05:05.837
I had 18 boyfriends
before this, you know?

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:08.160
Deal.

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:21.160
(I had 18 boyfriends
before this, you know?)

00:05:23.180 --> 00:05:24.080
What card did you get?

00:05:24.080 --> 00:05:25.480
Oh no.

00:05:36.280 --> 00:05:37.280
Oh, you got 3 of Hearts.

00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:38.360
He got it.

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:39.920
They got it.

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:44.200
It's them.

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:45.800
Kiss!

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:54.480
- Kiss!
- Kiss!

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:55.480
Kiss her!

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:57.360
Kiss!

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:58.160
Enough.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:00.560
You can drink if you don't want to kiss.

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:01.400
Let's drink.

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:06.360
What's wrong with kissing?

00:06:06.360 --> 00:06:06.880
Fine by me.

00:06:07.480 --> 00:06:08.160
Come on.

00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:13.680
Kiss her.

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:20.400
- Kiss her!
- Kiss her!

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:40.200
One,

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:41.080
two,

00:06:41.080 --> 00:06:41.920
three,

00:06:41.920 --> 00:06:42.760
four,

00:06:44.000 --> 00:06:44.800
five,

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:49.320
eight,

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:53.400
15!

00:06:53.400 --> 00:06:53.960
Alright.

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:54.920
Time's up.

00:06:54.920 --> 00:06:55.720
Zhu, come.

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:56.880
Let's skip that game.

00:06:56.880 --> 00:06:58.000
I'll teach you how to roll dice.

00:06:58.000 --> 00:06:58.800
She's not playing.

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:02.360
Was I speaking to you?

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:06.760
It's been ten minutes.

00:07:06.760 --> 00:07:07.760
We should head home now.

00:07:10.760 --> 00:07:12.480
Ye Man, who do you think you are?

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:14.180
Why do you have to
stick your nose into everything?

00:07:14.420 --> 00:07:16.900
I'm her stepbrother.
Of course I can meddle with her affairs.

00:07:19.760 --> 00:07:21.012
Ze,

00:07:21.050 --> 00:07:22.680
why don't we come out again next time?

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:23.600
I'll head home first.

00:08:02.537 --> 00:08:03.177
Hello?

00:08:03.725 --> 00:08:05.525
I found some leads.

00:08:05.737 --> 00:08:06.777
Send them to me.

00:08:24.220 --> 00:08:25.520
This should be
the information you're looking for

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:26.560
from 19 years ago.

00:08:27.125 --> 00:08:29.700
The former dean
repeatedly urged its destruction,

00:08:29.710 --> 00:08:32.537
but it happened to coincide with
the renovation of the older hospital.

00:08:32.537 --> 00:08:33.737
That's why it still exists.

00:08:34.237 --> 00:08:36.740
But you have to promise me
that you won't get me in trouble.

00:08:39.537 --> 00:08:40.927
Don't worry about it, Mr. Chen.

00:08:49.450 --> 00:08:52.225
(Hai City People's Hospital)

00:08:53.962 --> 00:08:56.187
(Hai City People's Hospital)

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:02.000
Mr. Ye.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:04.040
19 years ago, Shen Qi suffered
severe hemorrhaging during childbirth.

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:06.000
But Lu Jiaming wasn't
at Hai City back then.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:08.600
Shen Qi had already sent her child away
by the time he came back.

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.440
Why did she send her own child away?

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.080
About that,

00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:14.840
I haven't identified the cause yet.

00:09:25.462 --> 00:09:26.782
Have some food.

00:09:28.840 --> 00:09:30.000
Have some water.

00:09:31.937 --> 00:09:33.817
Stop pretending.

00:09:33.960 --> 00:09:35.480
You're tired, and so am I.

00:09:36.680 --> 00:09:38.360
Tell me.

00:09:39.212 --> 00:09:41.132
What exactly are you up to?

00:09:41.132 --> 00:09:43.132
I just want to be nicer to you.

00:09:44.212 --> 00:09:46.972
I know it's difficult
to be a stepmother.

00:09:46.980 --> 00:09:49.990
Even so, I wish to make it up to you for
the motherly love you didn't receive.

00:09:51.080 --> 00:09:52.080
Motherly love?

00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:56.440
It sounds hilarious
when it's coming from you.

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:57.720
You know well enough

00:09:57.720 --> 00:09:59.560
why I lacked motherly love
in the first place.

00:09:59.560 --> 00:10:01.160
When my mother was pregnant,

00:10:02.120 --> 00:10:04.760
when she was seriously ill,

00:10:04.760 --> 00:10:07.200
you, as a close friend of hers,

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:09.040
ended up having an affair
with her husband.

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:12.640
You should save your energy.

00:10:12.640 --> 00:10:13.880
I'm not falling for it.

00:10:14.360 --> 00:10:15.680
Stay away from my son.

00:10:17.480 --> 00:10:19.560
Your father is my husband now.

00:10:19.560 --> 00:10:21.240
Ye Man is your elder brother.

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:23.662
You can seduce anyone you like,
except for Ye Man.

00:10:23.662 --> 00:10:25.262
Come at me if you wish to seek revenge.

00:10:25.887 --> 00:10:26.960
Don't try to touch Ye Man.

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:30.400
I see now.

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:34.800
Why should I listen to you?

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.440
You're back.

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:06.560
Elder brother,

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:09.080
you came back so late.

00:11:11.520 --> 00:11:13.720
Were you on a date with someone else?

00:11:15.937 --> 00:11:17.897
Why did you drink so much?

00:11:23.520 --> 00:11:25.480
Are you caring for me,

00:11:25.480 --> 00:11:26.640
Elder brother?

00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:37.160
Miss Lu, you picked up drawing
and piano from a young age.

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:40.440
You have never done any hard work.

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:42.160
Why are your fingers this coarse?

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:44.680
Stay out of my business.

00:11:47.240 --> 00:11:49.280
I'm the one asking you here.

00:11:53.475 --> 00:11:54.875
Anything you desire,

00:11:57.280 --> 00:11:58.520
I can give it to you.

00:12:25.625 --> 00:12:26.425
Is someone there?

00:12:41.520 --> 00:12:42.640
Does it hurt?

00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:46.160
That's more like it.

00:12:47.175 --> 00:12:48.575
I'm not someone to mess with.

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:52.040
What are you trying to do here?

00:12:52.040 --> 00:12:54.320
You'll know when you give it a try.

00:13:01.312 --> 00:13:05.812
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:13:06.037 --> 00:13:09.825
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:14.075
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:13:14.075 --> 00:13:18.212
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:13:18.337 --> 00:13:22.112
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:13:22.112 --> 00:13:25.887
♪I'll learn to stop
longing for what's gone♪

00:13:25.887 --> 00:13:28.162
♪The you in my memories♪

00:13:28.162 --> 00:13:30.175
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:13:30.175 --> 00:13:35.612
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:13:37.175 --> 00:13:42.612
♪Forget you completely♪